'''2020年ATP杯'''是首届[[ATP杯|ATP杯]]赛事，它是由[[职业网球联合会|职业网球联合会]]举办的国际性男子团体室外硬地网球赛事。作为[[2020年ATP巡回赛|2020年ATP巡回赛]]的揭幕战，这是自2012年上一届“世界团体赛”(World Team Cup)以来的首个ATP团体赛事。它于2020年1月3日至12日在澳大利亚城市[[布里斯班|布里斯班]]、[[珀斯|珀斯]]和[[悉尼|悉尼]]的三个场馆举行。

[[塞尔维亚|塞尔维亚]]在决赛中2:1击败了[[西班牙|西班牙]]队，获得首个ATP杯的冠军奖杯。<ref name=final>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2020/jan/12/novak-djokovic-serbia-defeats-rafael-nadal-spain-atp-cup|first=Kevin|last=Mitchell|title=Novak Djokovic leads Serbia to glory against Spain in inaugural ATP Cup|work=The Guardian|date=12 January 2020|access-date=2021-03-05|archive-date=2021-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210526145650/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2020/jan/12/novak-djokovic-serbia-defeats-rafael-nadal-spain-atp-cup}}</ref>

==赛事背景==

2018年7月2日，时任ATP总监克里斯·科莫德(Chris Kermode)宣布他计划组织一次男子团体网球比赛，此赛事是在六个月前[[台維斯盃|戴维斯杯赛]]宣布对比赛进行改革后提出的。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/tennis/43202373|title=Davis Cup: ITF plans to introduce 18-team World Cup of Tennis Finals in revamp|date=26 February 2018|access-date=16 September 2019|publisher=BBC|archive-date=2021-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211229160652/https://www.bbc.com/sport/tennis/43202373}}</ref> 

该赛事原本打算叫做“世界团体赛”(''World Team Cup'')，但因为和从1978年到2012年在[[杜塞尔多夫|杜塞尔多夫]]举行的世界团体(''World Team Cup'')名字相近。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/tennis/44676167|title=ATP World Team Cup: New 24-team tournament to launch in 2020|date=1 July 2018|access-date=16 September 2019|publisher=BBC|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109041703/https://www.bbc.com/sport/tennis/44676167}}</ref> 于是四个月后，即11月15日，[[澳大利亚网球协会|澳大利亚网球协会]]宣布该项赛事更名为ATP杯，二十四支球队将在澳大利亚三个城市进行比赛，为球员参加[[澳大利亚网球公开赛|澳网]]热身。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.atptour.com/en/news/atp-unveils-atp-cup-team-event-for-2020-season|title=ATP Unveils 'ATP Cup' Team Event For 2020 Season|date=15 November 2018|access-date=16 September 2019|publisher=ATP World Tour|archive-date=2019-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713171303/https://www.atptour.com/en/news/atp-unveils-atp-cup-team-event-for-2020-season}}</ref> 举办城市为悉尼、布里斯班和珀斯，而[[霍普曼盃|霍普曼杯]]则因新比赛而走入历史。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.abc.net.au/news/2019-03-28/hopman-cup-axed-to-be-replaced-by-atp-cup/10947582|title=Hopman Cup axed from Perth in favour of men's-only ATP Cup tournament|date=28 March 2019|access-date=16 September 2019|first=David|last=Weber|publisher=[[Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation|Australian Broadcasting Corporation]]|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107235440/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2019-03-28/hopman-cup-axed-to-be-replaced-by-atp-cup/10947582}}</ref>

