==参赛队伍==
2019年9月，根据ATP在9月9日的单打选手的世界排名情况和他们参加赛事的承诺，ATP球员累计排名前18位的国家获得了参加ATP杯的资格。主办国澳大利亚收到了一张外卡。由于[[罗杰·费德勒|罗杰·费德勒]]个人原因退出了该项赛事，排名第三的瑞士也退出了预选赛。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/tennis/50232523|title=Roger Federer pulls out of inaugural ATP Cup for 'personal reasons'|website=BBC|date=30 October 2019|access-date=2021-03-05|archive-date=2021-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524195746/https://www.bbc.com/sport/tennis/50232523}}</ref> 根据ATP在11月11日的ATP排名，最后6只队伍也获得了参赛资格。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.atptour.com/en/news/top-18-teams-announced-australia-atp-cup-2019|title=Top 18 Countries & World's Top 10 Commit To Play 2020 ATP Cup|website=ATP Tour|date=13 September 2019|access-date=2021-03-05|archive-date=2022-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220326034226/https://www.atptour.com/en/news/top-18-teams-announced-australia-atp-cup-2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.atptour.com/en/news/24-countries-field-set-for-atp-cup-2020|title=24-Country Field Set For Inaugural 2020 ATP Cup|website=ATP Tour|date=13 November 2019|access-date=2021-03-05|archive-date=2022-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220406222549/https://www.atptour.com/en/news/24-countries-field-set-for-atp-cup-2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.atptour.com/en/rankings/atp-cup-standings|title=ATP Cup Standings|website=ATP Tour|access-date=14 September 2019|archive-date=2021-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130141746/https://www.atptour.com/en/rankings/atp-cup-standings}}</ref>

